				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Th%C3%A1nh-T%C3%B4ng/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-phi%E1%BA%BFn-k%E1%BB%B3-08/poem-NcBZeng7qZnKnE0wICtVkA">Đề phiến kỳ 08 - 題扇其八</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Th%C3%A1nh-T%C3%B4ng/author-FSJg5-ivZkPUR1nhJkA6Fg">Lê Thánh Tông</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/M%C3%A3-T%E1%BB%95-Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/Gi%C3%A1-ph%C3%A1t-Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-Kinh/poem-ignOOt9-hec0jLvzdg9fXQ">Giá phát Thượng Kinh - 駕發上京</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/M%C3%A3-T%E1%BB%95-Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/author-yyTn7TVPngeU_4xv-pnSXQ">Mã Tổ Thường</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/H%E1%BA%A1-nh%E1%BA%ADt-thu%E1%BB%B5-kh%E1%BB%9Fi/poem-5pBTW1x8JDnClVz-00vALg">Hạ nhật thuỵ khởi - 夏日酷暑</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/author-l-NINz3JTJVTCX2aN0HlSQ">Thái Thuận</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Khi%E1%BB%83n-h%E1%BB%A9ng-ng%C5%A9-th%E1%BB%A7-II-k%E1%BB%B3-3-T%E1%BA%A5t-h%E1%BB%AFu-d%E1%BB%A5ng-nhi-c%C3%A1t/poem-hEYRqvcCEV3WEqUGfhtJ9Q">Khiển hứng ngũ thủ (II) kỳ 3 (Tất hữu dụng nhi cát) - 遣興五首其三（漆有用而割）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/Kim-nh%E1%BA%ADt-h%C3%A0nh/poem-oPndryETiAPYBfAkUx3vow">Kim nhật hành - 今日行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/K%E1%BB%B3-%C3%BAc-2/poem-Fb9iKQ84kPvMS5KYYIAOWQ">Kỳ úc 2 - 淇奧 2</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/L%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Hoa-Th%E1%BB%8Bnh-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-qu%C3%A2n-th%C4%83ng-nh%E1%BA%ADm-ph%C3%B3-t%C6%B0-l%E1%BB%87nh/poem-k9TPoySkwG4dUqVQXVw5jg">Lương Hoa Thịnh tướng quân thăng nhậm phó tư lệnh - 梁華晟將軍升任副司令</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/author-a7YEflJr1_rcFKC9dgECgQ">Hồ Chí Minh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Ng%C6%B0-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/poem-jOxsKlqQzseVFjGMd6TMtQ">Ngư Dương - 漁陽</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-Dung/T%E1%BA%A1p-thi/poem-_ndqYlYTzi2tiRTwGhClNg">Tạp thi - 雜詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-Dung/author-DbWbkpTHsQKADNkIPT7sUw">Khổng Dung</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Tr%C3%A1ng-du/poem-dLYEgwcQ7IbIIq24Mpcddw">Tráng du - 壯遊</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
